      <h1>Comment ça marche ?</h1>
      <div class ="flexing">
        <div class = "card2">
          <h1>1. <strong>Mesurez</strong> l'impact de vos produits</h1>
          <br>
          <div class = "circle-around">
            <div class = "circle-inner">
              <i class="heart fas fa-weight"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
